%F A002322 If M = 2^e*P1^e1*P2^e2*...*Pk^ek, lambda(2^e) = 2^(e-1) if e=1 or 2, = 2^(e-2) if e > 2; lambda(M) = lcm(lambda(2^e), (P1-1)*P1^(e1-1), (P2-1)*P2^(e2-1), ..., (Pk-1)*Pk^(ek-1)).
